#TimePicker.  We make these keys somewhat similar to what the legacy AXML control did, just so our keys blend in somewhat.
dispatch.timeRange.earliest = (Added by Sideview).  Legacy - This is an older form of the earliest time argument used by the Sideview  "TimePicker" module.
dispatch.timeRange.latest = (Added by Sideview).  Legacy - This is an older form of the latest time argument used by the Sideview  "TimePicker" module.

dispatch.timeRange.<things> = (Added by Sideview).  This is for the newer earliest/latest time arguments of the timerange that the user has set in the "TimePicker" module in the Canary UI, in this particular view.

display.results.<things> =  (Added by Sideview).  Some modules write their moduleId in here to support cases where the page has more than one of the given module class.
